		<element name="Shield of Missile Attraction" type="Magic Item" source="Dungeon Master’s Guide" id="ID_WOTC_DMG_MAGIC_ITEM_SHIELD_OF_MISSILE_ATTRACTION">
			<description>
				<p>While holding this shield, you have resistance to damage from ranged weapon attacks.</p>
				<p><strong>Curse.</strong> This shield is cursed. Attuning to it curses you until you are targeted by the <em>remove curse</em> spell or similar magic. Removing the shield fails to end the curse on you. Whenever a ranged weapon attack is made against a target within 10 feet of you, the curse causes you to become the target instead.</p>
			</description>
			<setters>
				<set name="keywords">shield</set>
